These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, iced-tea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, electronic
1. the fan of r&b is the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is between the fan of electronic and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | fanta | iced-tea | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | r&b     | jazz    | electronic   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, writing, magic-tricks
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, software-developer, bartender
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the bartender is between the project-manager and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | puzzles    | magic-tricks        | writing |
| Job     | software-developer | bartender | project-manager         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, lemonade
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, pony, rat
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking water is between the owner of the pony and the person drinking lemonade##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | water     | lemonade |
| Pet        | pony  | rat | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, techno, house
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, snake, rat
1. the fan of indie is the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the fan of house is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the rabbit##2
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | house     | indie |
| Pet           | snake | rat | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking, camping
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, pony, hamster
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the pony##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | camping     | baking |
| Pet     | hamster    | hedgehog | pony    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, italian, argentine
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, soccer, rugby
1. the person who's sport is handball is between the argentine and the indonesian##2
2. the indonesian is the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the italian is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | italian   | argentine        |
| Sport         | soccer | handball | rugby |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, apple, peach
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, british, colombian
1. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
2. the canadian is between the person eating peach and the british##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | apple  | watermelon  | peach |
| Nationality   | british | canadian | colombian     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, musical, documentary
There are 3 different nationalities: american, pakistani, canadian
1. the person watching musical movies is the canadian##1
2. the pakistani is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching documentary movies##2
3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary   | spy  | musical  |
| Nationality   | american | pakistani | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, volleyball, badminton
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, bike, boat
1. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person driving the car is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person driving the bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | badminton | rugby | volleyball  |
| Transport   | boat    | car        | bike |

