.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, water
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, strawberry, apple
1. the person eating apple is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person eating nectarine##2
2. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee      | water      |
| Food       | strawberry  | apple | nectarine |

