2. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is surfing##2
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | techno | punk   | metal   |
| Sport         | surfing | handball | sailing |

