.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, jazz, techno
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the fan of jazz##2
3. the fan of funk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | funk | jazz   |

 